    "description": {
      "gm": "",
      "value": "<p><strong>Frequency</strong> once per day per affliction</p><hr /><p>Your soul becomes fuel, burning away your life force to stem the tide. Choose an affliction on yourself, such as a curse, disease, or poison. Lose a number of Hit Points equal to the level of the affliction. Make a new saving throw against the affliction as though you were at the end of its listed interval. If you roll a failure on this save, then there is no effect. If you roll a critical failure on this save, you get the failure result instead.</p>"
